verbose_text: The results demonstrated that miR-1246, miR-20a, miR-2392, miR-3147, miR-3162-5p, miR-4484 and miR-4667-5p were all expressed in the serum, and that their expression levels in serum were consistent with their expression levels in cervical tissue.
evidence: miR-3162-5p, miR-4484 and miR-4667-5p were all expressed
